text:
Well... as Steak 'n Shake locations go, this isn't the best one around--but it is burgers and fries that are open 24-7.

The milkshakes are good!

PROS: 
Always made fresh, when you order;

CONS:
Greasy (but its burgers);
Takes longer than typical in drive thru (but that's bc they're made fresh!);
Service (on a scale of 1-10, 10 being awesome) is a 4.
